videos.description: Alex Robinson blows by his defender on his way to a tough layup for the Horned Frogs.
videos.headline: TCU's Robinson attacks the rim

videos.description: Dean Wade knocks down the shot from beyond the arc for the Wildcats in the first half.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Wade splashes home 3-pointer

videos.description: Mike McGuirl gets the ball stolen from him but hustles back on defense and comes up with the big block for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kansas State's McGuirl denies TCU

videos.description: Cartier Diarra blows by his defender and gets the layup to fall despite getting fouled in the process.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Diarra drives the lane for tough layup

videos.description: TCU head coach Jamie Dixon is ejected in the second half for the Horned Frogs.
videos.headline: Dixon ejected in second half

videos.description: Dean Wade gets the dish from Barry Brown and finishes with authority for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Wade throws down two handed-slam

videos.description: Barry Brown drives down the lane and gets the floater to fall with 3 seconds to go on the shot clock.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Brown drops in floater

videos.description: Reid Gettys and Mitch Holthus breakdown the Wildcats' solid team performance that lead them to a 73-68 win over TCU.
videos.headline: Kansas State gets second win over a top 25 team in 5 days
